			"level": 1,
			"entries": [
				"你的魔法与大自然的美丽和优雅联系在一起。也许你是从一个神秘的干尸那里获得的魔法，或者是偶然发现了一个古老的森林仪式。无论你是如何获得的，你都能在你创造的花朵中体现这种美，以保护你的盟友。",
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Orchard Magic|Sorcerer||Orchard|OrchardSorcReflourished|1"
				},
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Inspiring Bloom|Sorcerer||Orchard|OrchardSorcReflourished|1"
				},
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Garden Chatter|Sorcerer||Orchard|OrchardSorcReflourished|1"
				}
			]
		},
